                      <p></p><div class="metafield-rich_text_field"><ul><li>Designed to fit 2007+ Mercedes Sprinter 144&quot; WB, 170&quot; WB and 170&quot; WB EXT low and high-roof vans.</li><li>Single-pane glass automotive window with a sliding panel and removable sliding screen, locking latch</li><li>Bond-in installation</li><li>Manufactured by <a href="http://amauto.co.uk/" target="_blank">AM Auto</a></li><li>Solar privacy glass with 17% tint (also known as <a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Factory_tint" target="_blank">&quot;factory tint&quot;</a>), matches Mercedes factory glass and conforms to AS3 standard</li><li>Meets European and North American standards, tested and certified to <a href="https://op.europa.eu/en/publication-detail/-/publication/6d819756-93c0-11e3-bf99-01aa75ed71a1" target="_blank">ECE R43</a> and North American (<a href="https://www.law.cornell.edu/cfr/text/49/571.205#:~:text=The%20purpose%20of%20this%20standard,the%20vehicle%20windows%20in%20collisions." target="_blank">US DOT FMVSS 205</a>/<a href="https://tc.canada.ca/en/corporate-services/acts-regulations/motor-vehicle-safety-regulations-crc-c-1038" target="_blank">Transport Canada CMVSS 205</a>) standards </li><li> <strong>6 month warranty</strong></li></ul></div>
                      
